{"lastModified":1749149852471,"uri":"c::7819198761::vessel::d5cc4d39-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Italy\n\nMotoryacht Angra Too , built in 2015 with its 38 meters in length and 8.10 meters in width, is the largest wooden boat to come out of the Castagnola shipyards. It offers beautiful accommodation for up to 11 guests in 6 cabins: 3 doubles, 2 twins and 1 single. The interiors, developed by the architects Andrea Borzelli and Sara Berta as well as the external lines, together with Giovanni Castagnola, have ample space and great livability, both in the living and sleeping areas. The main deck offers a huge salon at the stern, in direct communication with the outside, a lounge and a wet bar. Motoryacht Angra Too benefits from some excellent features to enhance your charter, for example it has a gym with all the latest equipment to keep your fitness routine active. Motoryacht ANGRA TOO 38 mt is also equipped with stabilizers at anchor and during navigation, wifi, A / C and an extraordinary terrace on the fly of 65 m2. An attentive and professional crew of 6 people will take care of every single detail on board.","blueprint":{"name":"ANGRA TOO","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d39-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::83ab1580-40ae-11f0-bc77-5dec5b281ab2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d39-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9c3a9ee0-40ae-11f0-872b-a74dc148eb07/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d39-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9c0229c0-40ae-11f0-872b-a74dc148eb07/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d39-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9c049ac0-40ae-11f0-872b-a74dc148eb07/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d39-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9c016670-40ae-11f0-872b-a74dc148eb07/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc4d39-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::9c43edb0-40ae-11f0-9475-af5dc82b0c96/{i